Note on data and third-party content:

- Stellar and exoplanet measurement values aggregated in `db/` are
  derived from public astronomical catalogs (NASA Exoplanet Archive,
  Gaia DR3, SIMBAD, TEPCat). These values are factual data and are not
  subject to this license. Citations are documented in
  `docs/reference/data-sources.md`.

- Excerpts of Sol-Configs (https://github.com/RSS-Reborn/Sol-Configs) in
  `.agents/skills/kopernicus-cfg/references/` are reproduced for
  documentation purposes only. Sol-Configs has no published license as
  of 2026-05-19; explicit permission from the maintainer is pending.
  See `docs/reference/data-sources.md` §2.

- References to Kopernicus (LGPL-3.0) in this repository are descriptive
  only; no Kopernicus source code is reproduced here.
